Casino’s Exito Is to Seek $1.4 Billion by Selling New Shares in Colombia

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-06-30T06:31:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/casino-s-exito-seeks-to-raise-1-4-billion-selling-new-shares-in-colombia.html
Casino Guichard-Perrachon SA (CO) ’s Exito
unit will seek to raise as much as $1.4 billion by selling new
shares in  Colombia .  Casino will subscribe in line with its 54.8 percent stake
and will keep control of Exito, it said in a statement. Exito is
purchasing Casino’s stakes in Disco and Devoto for $746 million,
the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  